                    <div class="tour_head1">
                        <h3>Description</h3>
                        <p>Mombasa Continental Resort is a Five Star hotel located on Shanzu Beach on the North Coast in Mombasa Kenya, 18kms from the Airport and 13kms from the city centre. The resort seats on 8.3 acres of beautifully landscaped gardens with 300m white beach front view of the Indian Ocean with a total of 183 sea facing rooms with breathtaking views in all the 5 categories. 3 Presidential Suites,6 Junior Suites, 93 Twin rooms ,73 King size rooms, 2 Handicap room</p>
