                    <div class="tour_head1 l-info-pack-days days">
                        <h3>Detailed Day Wise Itinerary</h3>
                        <ul>
                                                        <li class="l-info-pack-plac"> <i class="fa fa-clock-o" aria-hidden="true"></i>
                                <h4><span>Before Traveling To Mombasa</span> </h4>
                                <p>Our Bonfire Adventures Agent will book your SGR Ticket for you. After booking the ticket, the reference number will be sent to you either via Email or WhatsApp. You can then print the ticket on the day of travel at the SGR Station. </p>
                            </li>
                                                        <li class="l-info-pack-plac"> <i class="fa fa-clock-o" aria-hidden="true"></i>
                                <h4><span>Before Traveling To Mombasa</span> </h4>
                                <p>Our Bonfire Adventures Agent will book your SGR Ticket for you. After booking the ticket, the reference number will be sent to you either via Email or WhatsApp. You can then print the ticket on the day of travel at the SGR Station. </p>
                            </li>
                                                        <li class="l-info-pack-plac"> <i class="fa fa-clock-o" aria-hidden="true"></i>
                                <h4><span>DAY 1: </span> NAIROBI TO MOMBASA</h4>
                                <p>The transfer from your home or hotel to the Nairobi SGR Station at Syokimau will be on your own arrangement. You are required to depart from Nairobi as per the SGR timing booked. The SGR train ride is not just a train ride but a cruise with the chance to spot the wildlife as you pass through Tsavo National Park.  
As soon as you arrive to the Mombasa Terminus you will meet our trusted and reliable agent. He will help you with your luggage and drive you from the Mombasa Terminus to your hotel. 
Once you check into your hotel, feel free to relax. Enjoy the hotel amenities such as the pool, the gardens, relax under the palm trees and enjoy exciting beach activities. If you would like you can step out and enjoy the city of Mombasa. 
	Meals And Drinks As Per The Hotel Chosen 
</p>
                            </li>
                                                        <li class="l-info-pack-plac"> <i class="fa fa-clock-o" aria-hidden="true"></i>
                                <h4><span>DAY 1: </span> NAIROBI TO MOMBASA</h4>
                                <p>The transfer from your home or hotel to the Nairobi SGR Station at Syokimau will be on your own arrangement. You are required to depart from Nairobi as per the SGR timing booked. The SGR train ride is not just a train ride but a cruise with the chance to spot the wildlife as you pass through Tsavo National Park.  
As soon as you arrive to the Mombasa Terminus you will meet our trusted and reliable agent. He will help you with your luggage and drive you from the Mombasa Terminus to your hotel. 
Once you check into your hotel, feel free to relax. Enjoy the hotel amenities such as the pool, the gardens, relax under the palm trees and enjoy exciting beach activities. If you would like you can step out and enjoy the city of Mombasa. 
	Meals And Drinks As Per The Hotel Chosen 
</p>
                            </li>
                                                        <li class="l-info-pack-plac"> <i class="fa fa-clock-o" aria-hidden="true"></i>
                                <h4><span>DAY 2  DAY 3: </span> IN MOMBASA</h4>
                                <p>Nothing beats a day at the beach. The warm sand, soothing sound of waves and the sea breeze.  Science says the sea and sand does the mind (and body) good. These days spent in Mombasa are the perfect way to reap all the benefits of vitamin sea.

Mombasa is one of the most relaxing and exciting vacation spots that you can imagine. If youre an adventure seeker, how about spending your time enjoying boat rides, jet-skiing, kite surfing or any other exciting beach activity offered at your own cost. If youd love to calm your soul with lazy days at the beach, how about lounging by the beach or the hotel pool and soak in your well-deserved vacation days with a cool drink and gorgeous view. 
</p>
                            </li>
                                                        <li class="l-info-pack-plac"> <i class="fa fa-clock-o" aria-hidden="true"></i>
                                <h4><span>DAY 4: </span> LAST DAY IN MOMBASA AND DEPARTURE TO NAIROBI</h4>
                                <p>This will be your final vacation day in Mombasa. After breakfast you can enjoy a few moments at the hotel. Take a dip in the pool and the beach, sip a cool drink and soak in the sun. 

Our trusted agent will drive to the hotel in good time and drive you to the Standard Gauge Railway (Mombasa Terminus). We guarantee that you will arrive at the station right in time for the departure to Nairobi. As soon as you get to the city, the transfer back to your home will be as per your own arrangement. </p>
                            </li>
                                                    </ul>
                    </div>



